#T ##  \item Define the homomorphism $\pi$ by computing the images $\pi(g)$
#T ##        for $g$ in a generating set of $N$.
#T ##        This is again independent of $\chi$.
#T ##  
#T ##  \item Compute $\bigcap_{j\in J} Stab_{\pi(N)}(\tilde{O}_j)$.
